                                                      "ol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Explores predefined downloadable examples of scenes of the digital world of spiders and ants to build important dependencies:</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">How does the speed of ants and spiders affect the results of the system;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">How does the vision radius of ants and spiders affect the results of the system;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">How does the energy consumption of an ant and a spider affect the results of the system;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><spa"
                                                      "n style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Complicate the process of making collective decisions of ants to evaluate their impact on the results of the system:</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Ants act purely individually, without any collective interaction;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Ants gather in teams to bring large amounts of food together;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Ants form a team to fight spiders;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</sp"
                                                      "an><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Create conditions under which ants win;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Create conditions under which spiders win;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Create conditions where a balance is established between ants and spiders;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Create conditions where the number of ants and spiders oscillates rhythmically;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Show and explain other inter"
                                                      "esting phenomena you discovered.</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;\">6. Prospects</span></p><p align=\"justify\">The system is under development now but is intended for step-by-step way application at the following levels: </p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;\">Stage 1</span><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:700;\"> \u2013 </span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">obtaining a first understanding of multi-agent systems and studying the processes of self-organization in complex systems such as natural ecosystems, in which processes of competition and cooperation of participants are observed;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman',"
                                                      "'serif'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;\">Stage 2 </span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">\u2013 obtaining a first understanding of ontologies that help build formalized knowledge models of domain areas and use the ontologies for setting up and developing multi-agent systems;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol';\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;\">Stage 3</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">\u2013 studying the basics of multi-agent programming and expanding the world of the proposed system through the introduction of new proprietary software agents of the participants and protocols for their interaction;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol';\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;\">Stage 4</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman',"
                                                      "'serif'; font-size:12pt;\">\u2013 study and development of models and methods for collective decision-making of agents to achieve a state of \u201ccompetitive equilibrium\u201d (consensus).</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;\">7. Technical requirements</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Below is a list of recommended application server hardware and software requirements:</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">RAM: 8 GB or more;</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Symbol'; font-size:12pt;\">\u00b7</span><span style=\" font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12pt;\">Python 3 with installed libraries:</span></p><p align=\"justify\"><span style=\" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;\">o</span><span"
